How leadgen works

STEP 1

Onboarding setup

Together we dive deep into your business domain, market niche and put together Ideal Customer Profile.
STEP 2

DATA RESEARCH

Combining experienced data researchers and smart tools, we can identify hundreds of potential Clients per week.
STEP 3

DESIGN OUTREACH CAMPAIGN

We set up a targeted campaign to touch Clients via email, LinkedIn, socials or phone. You will only need to respond to the warm leads who are highly interested.
STEP 4

CONTINUOUS IMPROVEMENT. A/B TESTING

You will obtain hot leads daily. But we don't stop improving and optimizing smart outreach. Your Data Journey starts here.
STEP 5

DEDICATED TEAM

The main goal is to build an effective distributed sales team. Train your own ninjas and reap all the benefits of your own leadgen Army.
